The former Walter Sisulu University student found guilty of stealing over R800,000 returns to court for pre-sentencing. Up to R1.4m was mistakenly deposited into her account by NSFAS, and she proceeded to spend over R800,000 of it.  JOHANNESBURG - The former Walter Sisulu University student found guilty of stealing over R800,000 returns to court for pre-sentencing. Up to R1.4m was mistakenly deposited into her account by NSFAS, and she proceeded to spend over R800,000 of it.